                <head>313. Summary of Conclusions of a Presidential Review Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d313fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                        Security Council, Institutional Files, 1977–1981, Box 68, <gloss
                            target="#t_PRC_1">PRC</gloss> 056: Philippines Base Issues, 2/28/78.
                        Secret. The meeting took place in the White House Situation Room. <persName
